# Frame Assets Directory

Place all 189 avatar frames in this directory.

Frames should be named:
- ezgif-frame-001.jpg
- ezgif-frame-002.jpg
- ...
- ezgif-frame-189.jpg

These will be automatically served by Next.js and loaded into the canvas animation.

For quick setup, run:
- **Windows**: `setup.bat`
- **macOS/Linux**: `bash setup.sh`

Both scripts will automatically move frames from the root directory to this location.
